106
00:05:37,103 --> 00:05:39,231
Yes. Exactly.

107
00:05:39,606 --> 00:05:40,883
How long do you
think this Max guy

108
00:05:40,907 --> 00:05:43,001
can shake things up
before the Dean steps in?

109
00:05:43,109 --> 00:05:46,079
Not long. Dean of medicine
does not like things shaken up,

110
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:48,606
based on my
extensive experience.

111
00:05:48,782 --> 00:05:50,182
All right.

112
00:05:56,590 --> 00:06:01,153
How you doing? I'm Dr. Frome.
But you can call me Iggy, all right?

113
