119
00:06:15,942 --> 00:06:17,535
Okay.

120
00:06:17,677 --> 00:06:19,373
No big deal, you know?

121
00:06:19,479 --> 00:06:21,505
We can get to the
bottom of this, easy-peasy.

122
00:06:21,781 --> 00:06:23,181
Okay?

123
00:06:27,954 --> 00:06:29,394
Let's see what
we're looking at here.

124
00:06:29,689 --> 00:06:33,717
All right, says here you've been
on Zotepine for the last few years?

125
00:06:35,061 --> 00:06:36,154
Is that right?

126
00:06:38,064 --> 00:06:40,295
Did something happen at school?

127
00:06:41,301 --> 00:06:44,465
No? You sure about that?
'Cause zotepine, my friend, that is...

128
00:06:45,305 --> 00:06:47,137
That's big-time.
That is no joke.

129
00:06:48,842 --> 00:06:50,811
Nothing happened that
you want to tell me about?

130
00:06:51,077 --> 00:06:52,409
No.

131
00:06:52,679 --> 00:06:54,477
Okay, cool. Fair enough.

132
00:06:55,048 --> 00:06:57,142
All right. They've
also got you on

133
00:06:57,350 --> 00:06:59,842
Sertraline. Huh.

134
00:07:04,224 --> 00:07:06,090
And Zolpidem.

135
00:07:07,093 --> 00:07:09,562
Oh, my gosh, they have
