Dean of medicine
called again. Pass.

159
00:08:29,142 --> 00:08:31,134
You can't keep
ignoring him, Max.

160
00:08:31,244 --> 00:08:33,589
When you fire half the staff,
disembowel an entire hospital,

161
00:08:33,613 --> 00:08:35,573
you have to expect your
boss is gonna be on you...

162
00:08:35,615 --> 00:08:37,447
To what? Re-bowel it?

163
00:08:38,284 --> 00:08:39,752
Sounds gross, doesn't it?

164
00:08:39,819 --> 00:08:41,117
Max!

165
00:08:41,421 --> 00:08:43,913
Dr. Sharpe, back in the
trenches. How's re-entry?

166
00:08:43,990 --> 00:08:45,014
I wouldn't know.

167
00:08:45,125 --> 00:08:46,235
You didn't show up to your
appointment this morning.

168
00:08:46,259 --> 00:08:48,956
Well, I had a department chair
meeting. Which you missed, I believe.

169
00:08:49,029 --> 00:08:50,622
Because we had an appointment.

170
00:08:50,697 --> 00:08:52,074
What? How... Did
I forget something?

171
00:08:52,098 --> 00:08:54,465
No, no, just, Dr. Sharpe
and I have a little thing.

172
00:08:54,534 --> 00:08:56,002
Very informal.

173
