It's not informal.
It's quite serious.

174
00:08:58,138 --> 00:09:00,039
How serious? Not
very. I'm taking care of it.

175
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:01,164
Are you? Mmm-hmm.

176
00:09:01,274 --> 00:09:02,298
Have you eaten today?

177
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:03,638
Does espresso count?

178
00:09:03,810 --> 00:09:05,421
Dora, would you mind
getting him an apple?

179
00:09:05,445 --> 00:09:07,209
An apple? Mmm.
He'll be in my office.

180
00:09:07,313 --> 00:09:08,872
I can't. I got a full schedule.

181
00:09:08,982 --> 00:09:10,541
Your 2:00 p.m. just canceled.

182
00:09:10,784 --> 00:09:12,150
Thank you, Dora.

183
00:09:12,485 --> 00:09:14,317
Thought you were
getting me an apple.

184
00:09:16,856 --> 00:09:19,052
Max. You have can...
We have 1,500 patients.

185
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:21,321
I don't have time
to be one of them.

186
00:09:22,228 --> 00:09:25,392
You better find the time
before you run out of it.

187
00:09:30,370 --> 00:09:32,681
One of the valves that
controls the flow of blood

188
